snippet.title: WARSAW | WWII Tactical RPG | PC Release Date Trailer
snippet.description:
WARSAW is a brand new tactical rpg set in a war-torn European capital during WWII. Wishlist it on Steam:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/1026420/WARSAW/

PC version coming out on 4th of September, console versions to follow.

Homepage: http://warsawthegame.com/
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/Warsawthegam...
Twitter: https://twitter.com/warsawthegame
